- `chat-auto-parser-generator.cpp` - Automatic parser generation

### 2. **Data Structures**

**Core Input/Output Types:**

```cpp
struct common_chat_templates_inputs {
    std::vector<common_chat_msg> messages;
    std::string grammar;
