**Currently Registered Handlers (7 total):**
1. `common_chat_params_init_ministral_3()` - Mistral/Magistral Large 3
2. `common_chat_params_init_gpt_oss()` - GPT-OSS (openai-moe)
3. `common_chat_params_init_functionary_v3_2()` - Functionary v3.2
